n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc0276541ce5b11e669bc18ffbba08c2024d479","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好寫實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如有雷同，實屬不幸。"},{"pid":"4c39fcdd800bc84c4336e7cc8579ccacd6de9a75","tid":91213,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:52:36.000Z","msg":"好亂 我追邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是咪可以facebook睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64a8554670219951a85af83a11a5c3d8c50e7b2","tid":91213,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好亂 我追邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是咪可以facebook睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  原來有link"},{"pid":"ee93c6ef07979e279f7a9b2021caf034ab66d998","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"阿瑩推開我，攬住我嫲嫲：「我知您得祥仔一個孫，<br />\n您地感情咁好，您都想佢成家立室......」<br />\n<br />\n阿瑩愈講愈細聲，我靜係聽到最後果句：<br />\n「您八十幾歲，除咗呢件事，都無野可以幫到祥仔，<br />\n第日周身病痛仲連累佢。」<br />\n<br />\n阿瑩好滿意咁鬆開嫲嫲，去同地產經紀講野。<br />\n<br />\n而我，見到嫲嫲呆晒，我唔知講咩好。<br />\n<br />\n老豆死後，我無錢交租，住喺阿瑩屋企，日日畀佢阿媽嘲諷。<br />\n我都好大壓力，好想......買樓。<br />\n<br />\n就係果一下猶豫，嫲嫲突然衝出露台，<br />\n用拐杖一撐，連爬帶滾咁跌咗落去。<br />\n<br />\n我從來無見過嫲嫲咁靈活，<br />\n十八樓，粉身碎骨。<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n我喊咗好耐，但等警察調查完，確定嫲嫲係自殺，將個單位解封果日，<br />\n我同阿瑩都係拎住支票，去地產公司落訂。<br />\n<br />\n「對唔住，個單位已經畀呢位太太訂咗。」<br />\n<br />\n阿瑩捉住經紀：「咩話？你尋晚打畀我地，<br />\n話個單位平咗一半，叫我地今日落訂架！」<br />\n<br />\n「呢位太太肯畀七成，即係三百五十萬。」經紀指住隔離個女人。<br />\n<br />\n個女人不屑咁望住我地：「你地未落訂，梗係價高者得。<br />\n如果你地畀八成，賣家都會撻我訂，賣畀你地。點啊，有無錢？」<br />\n<br />\n如果我有咁多錢，嫲嫲就唔使死。<br />\n<br />\n阿瑩尖叫：「果間兇宅黎！妳買黎做乜？」<br />\n<br />\n「我知，有個鄉下婆怕老，跳樓死咗。<br />\n自殺啫，怨氣唔重，最多封咗個露台，兇殺我就驚啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「果個係我嫲嫲......」我就黎喊出聲。<br />\n<br />\n個女人嗤笑一聲：「依加法例規定，家屬可以平價買兇宅？<br />\n政府做帛金畀你？」　<br />\n<br />\n我嫲嫲......就咁死咗。<br />\n<br />\n層樓......俾人買咗。<br />\n<br />\n「我可唔可以上多一次去，拜吓我嫲嫲？」<br />\n<br />\n個女人勉為其難咁點頭：「好啦，記住叫你嫲嫲早啲投胎，唔好黎煩我。」<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n待續...<br />\nFB連載：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/tomato0728chan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftomato0728chan&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=211cfc3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/tomato0728chan</a>"},{"pid":"a4bf47215237006ea6c82638cfb8167b685c47ff","tid":91213,"uid":6455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"幾有趣 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59b3f854f75a2eb0a6f9a26da41ac101c23476e","tid":91213,"uid":59942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b9b9925a2ee8777041bc29354c1e6552bd7a4ad3","tid":91213,"uid":72122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97890594f10c3a30ae9ea7256aba14f6d0cccbe3","tid":91213,"uid":5726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e580b023d754922f86f9e8de03dc759763dfa99","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾有趣 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持！"},{"pid":"4ad6ea432d4df98e1d4d2d481c89d0ca17afb40d","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好少騎刧得咁工整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個故好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都無諗過會有師兄參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有趣"},{"pid":"a0b68b7fa8af3261d82134358de513f9c6225f11","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我等車無聊，騎劫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無諗過有人寫XD好開心，<br />\n師兄寫得幾有趣，我都好想知個經紀去咗邊，得閒可以寫埋佢，一人一個版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟獻醜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最強阿嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f2f6118d0dba9b0e8ee086bfd10a36cf8d0982","tid":91213,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"個女人真心痴撚線"},{"pid":"f90910e006a0b1e3e00041232c45d4625ccc20a1","tid":91213,"uid":34205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"09cbd78a4d964ee72767d8abd84653430263f059","tid":91213,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:34:30.000Z","msg":"我想睇死啊瑩個版本"},{"pid":"04da4a6cf4bb59af1d32e96ea543f3bf0c7b2008","tid":91213,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"我真係無睇錯，阿嫲推左阿瑩落街。<br />\n<br />\n我係窗口望住阿瑩背著我飛落街，望住佢四肢不由自主咁擺動，望住佢空中成功轉體180度，向住我瞪大對眼，露出左錯愕嘅表情。<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解我覺得佢呢一刻好滑稽。一個機關算盡嘅港女竟然比一個妹下妹下嘅阿婆暗算，就好似有大三巴既曼聯俾英甲仔屌打咁。<br />\n<br />\n一諗到呢度，我忍唔住「咭」一聲笑咗出嚟。（利申：阿狗）<br />\n<br />\n笑聲伴隨住地面「膨」一聲而結束，我呆住咁望地下果舊肉團，經紀同業主衝左入黎拉住我問咩事，我都無反應。直至阿嫲突然黎料，又將我拉回現實。<br />\n<br />\n「嗚嗚......點解你地個窗咁化學咖，未來家嫂挨一挨就自己打開左，佢無為意就跌左落去啦，你呢個殺人兇手！」說罷阿嫲就衝埋去個業主度，雙手扼住佢條頸，經紀手忙腳亂咁拉住佢......<br />\n<br />\n業主個樣好似林雪，佢聽完阿嫲咁講後成塊面白哂，即刻衝去窗口度向下望。自言自語：「呢獲仆街啦，一早叫左個衰婆整個爛鬼玻璃窗咖啦......」"},{"pid":"1be80a8b28681aa069fe8441f009b138eb117c63","tid":91213,"uid":58918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"正 個故有另一個平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fc04c86a7c25b26b1c2edf65cdfa55b60eddb7","tid":91213,"uid":65574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:57:42.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"649d980080e1a2142e338a9b9ef6eb6e778f98c9","tid":91213,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"騎劫仲好睇過樓主<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fed3e6cfca986fbf9295ea199b693488ad44f6","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>騎劫仲好睇過樓主<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪一齊欣賞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db050c09202a0611b7025759040410028d2fbe2","tid":91213,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"樓主果個其實係咪仲有一篇就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f546ee8b2ced94cd5619241f68c627df2961f1","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主果個其實係咪仲有一篇就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊，今晚up埋就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />短篇來的"},{"pid":"ddc719b09d4ec55650f5bf253216ba6621a10f74","tid":91213,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"本身想屌鳩樓上騎劫<br />\n但 仆街又幾好睇<br />\nBtw樓主加速"},{"pid":"152a4b0f3ba838f939fe2aac6849c3e3c81ee020","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想睇死啊瑩個版本</blockquote><br />\n係所有平行時空，阿瑩應該都要死..."},{"pid":"7a2e58074b072f8af8c6c3142764cf8da2b164f1","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"「我可唔可以上多一次去，拜吓我嫲嫲？」<br />\n<br />\n個女人勉為其難咁點頭：「好啦，記住叫你嫲嫲早啲投胎，唔好黎煩我。」<br />\n<br />\n經紀幫我開門，畀我同阿瑩入去：「我係樓下等你地，節哀順變。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿瑩望住間空屋，不斷講：「間屋本來係我地架！點解會買唔到？」<br />\n<br />\n「啪」一聲，阿瑩後腦流晒血，<br />\n<br />\n我用門後面枝掃帚棍，打咗佢一棍。<br />\n<br />\n「你痴咗線？」阿瑩尖叫，拎出電話正想報警。<br />\n<br />\n我一棍就打爛佢個電話，再一棍、再一棍，<br />\n佢俾我打到趴係度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「阿瑩，岩岩個女人話，兇殺佢就驚啦，兇殺......層樓會再平啲。」<br />\n<br />\n我一路講，一路扑，阿瑩愈黎愈細聲，無再辯駁，<br />\n睇黎佢接受我嘅解釋，佢都肯為買樓大業而犧牲，真係好老婆。<br />\n<br />\n掃帚棍斷咗，望住奄奄一息嘅阿瑩，我一腳踩落佢條頸度，<br />\n<br />\n咔嚓，大功告成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我搵到把剪刀，剪開佢嘅動脈，將啲血儘量塗喺牆上，<br />\n聽講兇宅場面愈恐怖，樓價愈低。<br />\n<br />\n我忙咗半日，成間屋都佈滿我嘅傑作，我身上嘅血都開始乾，<br />\n<br />\n門口傳來鎖匙聲，應該係經紀番黎搵我，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘿嘿，今次我仲唔買到樓？<br />\n<br />\n-完-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家支持呢個短篇！<br />\n<br />\nFB上有更多唔同嘅短篇故仔，<br />\n《男人一生，只為逃避一個喺麥記結婚嘅女人》：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Wy0KT3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWy0KT3&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=22a5256a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Wy0KT3</a><br />\n《為咗喺四季擺酒，我睇住老婆嫁比第二個男人》：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/nKQsqK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnKQsqK&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=925af533\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/nKQsqK</a><br />\n希望大家會鍾意！<br />\n<br />\n有咩意見都可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tomato0728chan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftomato0728chan&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=29ad2fcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tomato0728chan</a>"},{"pid":"6ccc7ae65a306552944e08e48895145966dc6715","tid":91213,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e4b425b12a2437c8b555630a01ea8f619f0ec1","tid":91213,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"其實阿嫲/阿爸/阿媽死左，層樓法定繼承人係事主，咁佢應該唔洗錢有2層樓喎"},{"pid":"40e26dd368a7ac288cae058fa4a76a463702e12d","tid":91213,"uid":21582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"baa8c4c064be161103a553e2aebaa54112187167","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實阿嫲/阿爸/阿媽死左，層樓法定繼承人係事主，咁佢應該唔洗錢有2層樓喎</blockquote><br />\n阿嫲從鄉下落黎，<br />\n而阿爸層樓係生意失敗，賣咗黎還債，怕刺激到情緒病嘅阿媽，阿爸求新業主租番畀佢，令佢地唔使搬。<br />\n事主唔知，以為阿爸有錢，（唔覺意）害死咗阿爸先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e838c6a6f8ed25d0b98dfaa6bab1d387a47b82","tid":91213,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"開個癡線佬台畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f6c4e32756d5b8dc81acd4d5310f61f6b8f50e","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開個癡線佬台畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈哈，有台咁好？不過女仔人家，叫佬好似唔係太切合。"},{"pid":"96edeea190d67a0ef212598928e1699f39a55580","tid":91213,"uid":8164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4c2313365352ecdc9218f5541c1d686eacab1d","tid":91213,"uid":70840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:26:22.000Z","msg":"睇完好不安<br />\n成件事好病態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ae31393dd24b945f971d65ab4ae3d6e3ddaff3","tid":91213,"uid":69987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:45:47.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f5ca63294a3e7b1817ad86530ad8548a2dfa32","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完好不安<br />\n成件事好病態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望現實唔會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貪念去到極點，就好難控制"},{"pid":"1eac6e19823e1b93a5b49d7691b36a788628d95b","tid":91213,"uid":58918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"唔錯 短得黎好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db59274af01f05581d62d6c414af1cb01c724c2","tid":91213,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿瑩死埋，已經完咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db38a51101a784ae3f0e281eaa8e2639f671e45","tid":91213,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"經紀幾經辛苦隔開左阿嫲同個業主，控制左個亂局後就即刻報警。<br />\n<br />\n五個警察幾分鐘就上到黎，阿嫲又捉住佢地喊哂咁講成件事，拎哂同情分，警方最後拉左林雪，話會檢控佢誤殺；又代我地通知阿瑩屋企人去認屍......講真......望住一舊肉團仲可以認到啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n不過，睇住林雪個人驚到震哂，個肚腩仲震到好似羅拔臣啫喱咁充滿喜感時，我又忍唔住「吱」一聲笑左出黎。<br />\n<br />\n警察拉左人後，阿嫲回復冷靜，問經紀咁樣搞到依家間屋變兇宅，仲邊有人買；又話橫掂林雪都要打官司，不如平少少賣左層樓俾我地去籌旗俾律師，一家便宜兩家着。<br />\n<br />\n經紀原本今日已經被玩謝，聽到有生意做之後又精神一振，即刻打電話俾林雪老婆傾下價。<br />\n<br />\n林雪老婆係警署度六神無主，最後俾個經紀氹掂，一層原本398萬既樓減到199萬就賣俾我。<br />\n<br />\n即日簽約，搞掂哂成件事後，阿嫲話同我去附近茶餐廳飲杯野傾兩句，話仲有手尾未完。<br />\n<br />\n而呢個手尾，必須由我去完成。<br />\n<br />\n經過今日，我發現佢先係Final Boss；呢位曾經最親、最熟悉既人，我已經望唔透。佢想同我傾計，我反而有種不寒而慄嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n佢到底仲想同我傾咩？<br />\n<br />\n我地入左間燈光昏黃嘅舊式茶餐廳，一坐度嗌左野飲，阿嫲就拎左張紙出黎，用支原子筆係上面寫左三組字：<br />\n<br />\n「連登」、「騎劫」、「陳美濤」。<br />\n<br />\n咩意思？我真係望唔透。"}]}